'''2011年洛爾卡地震'''（{{lang-es|'''Terremoto de Lorca de 2011'''}}，{{lang-en|'''2011 Lorca earthquake'''}}）是對[[西班牙|西班牙]][[穆爾西亞自治區|穆爾西亞自治區]]造成局部重大破壞的一起中等[[矩震級|矩震級]][[地震|地震]]。震央位於[[洛爾卡|洛爾卡]]鎮附近地下1公里（0.6英里）的淺層深度，發生於2011年5月11日[[歐洲中部夏令時間|歐洲中部夏令時間]]18:47（[[世界協調時|世界協調時]]16:47），導致當地陷入恐慌，許多房子因而位移。這起地震發生前還有一起於17:05 （15:05 UTC）引發，規模4.4（M<sub>w</sub>）的[[前震|前震]]，並對該地區的許多老舊結構物造成嚴重破壞，其中包括[[洛尔卡城堡|洛尔卡城堡]]歷史悠久的尖塔<ref>{{cite web |author=M. Carmen Cruz |url=http://www.rtve.es/noticias/20110511/minuto-minuto-dos-mujeres-embarazadas-entre-ocho-muertos-terremoto-lorca/431935.shtml |title=Minuto a minuto: El funeral por las víctimas será esta tarde en el recinto de Santa Quiteria |publisher=RTVE.es |date= |accessdate=2011-05-12 |archive-date=2015-06-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150604170332/http://www.rtve.es/noticias/20110511/minuto-minuto-dos-mujeres-embarazadas-entre-ocho-muertos-terremoto-lorca/431935.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>。有三個人遭到一塊掉落的[[簷口|簷口]]砸中而喪生<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.elpais.com/articulo/espana/terremotos/sacuden/Lorca/causan/muertos/elpepuesp/20110511elpepunac_38/Tes |title=Dos terremotos sacuden Lorca y causan ocho muertos · ELPAÍS.com |publisher=Elpais.com |date= |accessdate=2011-05-12 |archive-date=2011-05-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110520132158/http://www.elpais.com/articulo/espana/terremotos/sacuden/Lorca/causan/muertos/elpepuesp/20110511elpepunac_38/Tes |dead-url=no }}</ref>。經確認後總計有9人罹難，報導中約有幾十人受傷<ref name=guardian>{{cite news|last=Tremlett|first=Giles|title=Spain Shocked by Deadly Earthquake|url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/2011/may/12/spain-earthquake-havoc-questions|accessdate=2011-05-12|newspaper=The Guardian|date=2011-05-12|archive-date=2011-05-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110514192618/http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/2011/may/12/spain-earthquake-havoc-questions|dead-url=no}}</ref>。這起地震是自1956年[[格拉納達省|格拉納達省]][[阿尔沃洛特|阿尔沃洛特]]以西規模5.0（M<sub>w</sub>）的地震以來，該地區受創最嚴重的一次<ref name=worst>{{cite web|url=http://www.abc.es/20110511/sociedad/rc-seismo-lorca-causado-victimas-201105112010.html|title=El seísmo de Lorca, el que ha causado más víctimas desde 1956|work=[[ABC_(報紙)|ABC]]|author=[[埃菲通訊社|埃菲通訊社]]|date=2011-05-11|accessdate=2011-05-11|archive-date=2011-05-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110518150133/http://www.abc.es/20110511/sociedad/rc-seismo-lorca-causado-victimas-201105112010.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 地質 ==
[[File:2011_Lorca_earthquake_intensity.jpg|left]]
{{UTC time|歐洲中部夏令時間|+2}}
這起[[矩震級|矩震級]]5.1（M<sub>w</sub>）的內陸主震是發生於2011年5月11日當地時間18:47（16:47 UTC），震央大約在西班牙洛尔卡東北方2.5公里處，地下1公里（0.6英里）的極淺層震源<ref name=DETAILS /><ref name=emsc />。大多集中在[[伊比利半島|伊比利半島]]南部[[穆爾西亞自治區|穆爾西亞自治區]]的一部分，處於共同活躍地震的[[板塊構造|板塊構造]]帶上，當地的[[板塊構造#板塊的運動及邊界|板塊邊界]]推開[[歐亞板塊|歐亞板塊]]與[[非洲板塊|非洲板塊]]塑成現貌<ref name=geo /> 。然而，這地區絕大多數的顫動並未達到有感震級<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.europapress.es/sociedad/noticia-murcia-zona-habitual-movimientos-sismicos-no-dos-terremotos-registrados-miercoles-20110511195724.html|title=Murcia es una zone habitual de movimientos sísmicos pero no de los dos terremotos registrados este miércoles|work=[[歐洲通訊社|歐洲通訊社]]|date=2011-05-11|accessdate=2011-05-11|archive-date=2018-08-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180820141054/http://www.europapress.es/sociedad/noticia-murcia-zona-habitual-movimientos-sismicos-no-dos-terremotos-registrados-miercoles-20110511195724.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。據推測，這起地震直接導致[[阿拉馬_(穆爾西亞自治區)|阿拉馬]]主斷層（[http://www.agu.org/journals/ABS/2004/2002JB002359.shtml Alhama de Murcia fault]）附近[[走滑斷層|走滑斷層]]的產生<ref name=geo>{{cite web|url=http://earthquake.usgs.gov/earthquakes/recenteqsww/Quakes/usc0003c5s.php#summary|title=Magnitude 5.1 - Spain: Tectonic Summary|publisher=[[USGS|USGS]]|date=2011-05-11|accessdate=2011-05-11|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110608022652/http://earthquake.usgs.gov/earthquakes/recenteqsww/Quakes/usc0003c5s.php#summary|archivedate=2011-06-08}}</ref><ref name=Martínez-Díaz>{{Cite journal| doi = 10.4401/ag-3455| issn = 15935213| volume = 46| issue = 5| pages = 775-791| last = Martínez-Díaz| first = J. J.| coauthors = E. Masana, J. L. Hernández-Enrile, P. Santanach| title = Effects of repeated paleoearthquakes on the Alhama de Murcia Fault (Betic Cordillera, Spain) on the Quaternary evolution of an alluvial fan system| journal = ANNALS OF GEOPHYSICS| accessdate = 2011-05-12| date = 2003| url = http://www.earth-prints.org/handle/2122/989| archive-date = 2019-02-14| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190214074803/https://www.earth-prints.org/handle/2122/989| dead-url = no}}</ref>，這條沿線約有40至50公里（25至31英里）長的極淺斷層。當地專家也提出報告，斷層附近的表層有斷裂現象<ref name=fault>{{cite web|url=http://www.abc.es/agencias/noticia.asp?noticia=813703|title=Los dos seísmos se deben a un deslizamiento horizontal de falla de Lorca|work=[[American_Broadcasting_Company|ABC]]|author=[[埃菲通訊社|埃菲通訊社]]|date=2011-05-11|accessdate=2011-05-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110911212812/http://www.abc.es/agencias/noticia.asp?noticia=813703|archive-date=2011-09-11|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。最初[[美國地質調查局|美國地質調查局]]的預估是將地震排在規模5.3（M<sub>w</sub>）的震級<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.myfoxphoenix.com/dpps/news/world/four-dead-as-5.3-magnitude-earthquake-hits-southern-spain-dpgonc-20110511-to_13153597|title=Seven dead as moderate earthquake hits southern Spain|publisher=Fox Telivision Stations|work=myfoxphoenix.com|date=2011-05-11|accessdate=2011-05-11|archive-date=2012-03-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120309163113/http://www.myfoxphoenix.com/dpps/news/world/four-dead-as-5.3-magnitude-earthquake-hits-southern-spain-dpgonc-20110511-to_13153597|dead-url=no}}</ref>；[[歐洲地中海地震中心|歐洲地中海地震中心]]（EMSC）則報告震級烈度為5.2（[[芮氏地震規模|M<sub>L</sub>]]）<ref name=emsc>{{cite web|url=http://www.emsc-csem.org/Earthquake/earthquake.php?id=221132|title=Magnitude 5.2 - Spain - 2011-05-11 16:47 UTC|publisher=[http://www.emsc-csem.org/ EMSC]|date=2011-05-11|accessdate=2011-05-11|archive-date=2016-06-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160602231446/http://www.emsc-csem.org/Earthquake/earthquake.php?id=221132|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

由於綜合極淺層深度與中等震級兩項因素，地震造成了穆爾西亞多數地區劇烈地搖晃。而震央就在洛尔卡的不遠處，並記錄下強烈的地表運動，規模已達到[[麥加利地震烈度|麥加利地震烈度]]7級的最大值，至於當時不少臨近地區則報導為中等搖晃（MM V）<ref name=pager />。擴散出去的微顫據觀測來自於數百公里遠的震央，其中包括[[阿利坎特|阿利坎特]]（MM III）與[[馬德里|馬德里]]<ref name=pager /><ref>{{cite web |url=http://earthquake.usgs.gov/earthquakes/dyfi/events/us/c0003c5s/us/index.html |title=M5.1 - Spain |publisher=[[USGS|USGS]] |date=2011-05-11 |accessdate=2011-05-11 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110607023730/http://earthquake.usgs.gov/earthquakes/dyfi/events/us/c0003c5s/us/index.html |archivedate=2011-06-07 }}</ref> 。按統計，這次事件所釋放的地震能量（M<sub>e</sub>）相當於超過200公噸的[[三硝基甲苯|炸藥]]（TNT），大約是8.4×10<sup>11</sup>[[焦耳|焦耳]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://hypertextbook.com/facts/2002/AlexRoslyakov.shtml|title=Energy in a Ton of TNT|author=Revelle, D. O.|work=Global Infrasonic Monitoring of Large Meteorids|publisher=The Physics Factbook|date=2001|accessdate=2011-05-11|archive-date=2020-10-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201021014029/https://hypertextbook.com/facts/2002/AlexRoslyakov.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=energy>{{cite web|url=http://www.europapress.es/nacional/noticia-terremoto-amp-colegio-geologos-indica-seismo-equivale-mas-200-toneladas-tnt-20110511220541.html|title=(AMP) Colegio de Geólogos indica que el seísmo equivale a más de 200 toneladas de TNT|work=[[歐洲通訊社|歐洲通訊社]]|date=2011-05-11|accessdate=2011-05-11|archive-date=2012-10-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121006230546/http://www.europapress.es/nacional/noticia-terremoto-amp-colegio-geologos-indica-seismo-equivale-mas-200-toneladas-tnt-20110511220541.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

